node.text:
2019 was an incredible year for Cisco Brewers & we feel like we are on vacation EVERYDAY working, living and breathing Cisco Brewers... because we love our occupations. 🤙🥇💯
.
.
January 1, 2020 marks our 25th year as a brewery & we are so thankful to #CiscoNation for all the love & support. Here’s to another 25! 🍻❤️
.
Video credit to our boy @tweeddreams. You da man!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cisco Brewers in Cisco Brewers with @ackchamber, and @nantucketcurrent. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text:
Friends & family! We will begin requiring customers to show proof of a COVID-19 vaccination or a negative test before entering our Nantucket home base as of tomorrow, August 10. Stay safe 🤙🏼🍻! 

Proof of vaccination, proof of first dose or a negative test that will be accepted for entry include:

A physical vaccination card (name on the ID must match with the vaccination card).

A photo of the vaccination card on your phone (name on ID must match with vaccination card).

Results of a negative COVID-19 test within the past 72 hours (both antigen and PCR tests will be accepted).

Exceptions will be made for those not eligible for the vaccination (such as for kids under 12 years old).

#ciscobrewers #nantucket #newengland #staysafe #nicebeerifyoucangetit
